  "id": "RAW_7df56d20",
  "title": "Granola 创始人：如何打造一款首日跑通 PMF (产品市场契合点) 的产品？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485209&idx=1&sn=aa09ba4326ca98b719b5085c2e2e0425",
  "date": "2026-01-16 13:31:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=565a42c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaubJvugmGm13SvfIrwYw3IxSsPDv5s5vhciciazOLokDNJVkfwYVyFP8HHhuFTFNBseaUjHjIBr2ambaKYz4T05Q%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/player/player?podcastId=019bc6f6-42f2-7f0d-8493-5396e0ca6ee5&amp;openWithin=true\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听/4XNbRWRM8zetNhC\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/aubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24188790560471976\" data-w=\"1017\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"140\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f807faf8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FaubJvugmGm3MsjfMGwQrW2XnYZL7jFzPEsY0zs7ZE3ibia8qyHxNv6PhXphfbSicwmRPa2JSibzZEO5Kvh1iaXtEsvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></a></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style:italic;\">“用户不仅不知道自己想要什么，甚至不同用户的需求是完全冲突的。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style:italic;\">“只有砍掉那平庸的 50%，你才能集中精力将核心打磨成完美的钻石。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style:italic;\">“如果你需要 10 个人告诉你同一个按钮很困惑，那你就是在浪费时间。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在硅谷的创业叙事中，我们听惯了“精益创业”的故事：先发布一个粗糙的 MVP（最小可行性产品），然后在用户的吐槽中跌跌撞撞地迭代，最终在某个时刻由于运气或坚持，摸索到了产品市场契合点（PMF）。然而，AI 会议笔记工具 Granola 的创始人 Christopher Pedregal 却提供了一个不同的剧本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Granola 在发布的第一天就实现了 PMF。这不是运气，而是一场精心策划的结果。Christopher 坚信，PMF 不一定非要是发布后慢慢调整出来的，它完全可以通过特定的构建方式，在产品面世的那一刻就精准击中靶心。凭借这种策略，Granola 在短短一年半内从 4 人小团队扩张至 35 人，并以 2.5 亿美元的估值完成了 B 轮融资。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Christopher 的核心理念较为反直觉：在这个推崇“快速发布、快速失败”的时代，他选择了“慢下来”。他没有盲目地将半成品推向市场，而是通过深度的用户洞察和自我削减，确保产品在第一次面对公众时，就已经是一个拥有独立灵魂的“完成体”。接下来我们来拆解 Granola 是如何做到这一点的。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">打造用户最佳伙伴</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们常说某个产品“好用”，但很少说它有“灵魂”。在 Christopher 看来，这正是伟大产品与平庸产品的分水岭。当你拿起一个杯子，你与它的交互是物理的、直接的；但当你使用一款软件时，你实际上是在与设计者的思维进行交互。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“伟大的产品应该像人一样有性格、有价值观。当你与它交互时，应该感觉它是一致的、连贯的，而不是拼凑的。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个有灵魂的产品，应该像一个活生生的人，拥有性格、价值观和一致性。想象一下你最好的朋友，你大概能预判他在不同情境下的反应：如果你开他的玩笑，他会反击还是脸红？如果你赞美他，他会谦虚还是得意？这种预判基于你对他深层价值观的了解。如果你的朋友突然像你的小学校长一样说话，你会感到极度不适。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品也是如此。如果一个 App 的首页幽默风趣，但设置页面却官僚刻板，用户会感到一种潜意识的“认知失调”。这通常是“组织架构图式设计”的恶果，不同的页面由不同的部门负责，大家各行其是，导致产品充满了割裂感。Granola 从第一天起就极力避免这种情况，他们追求的是一种深层的连贯性：无论用户点击哪里，都能感受到同一个“人”在回应。这种统一的内核，就是用户能感知到的“灵魂”。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">50% 法则：在产品发布前将其精简一半</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Granola 最令人震惊的决策是在发布前夕。团队在正式发布前，实际上已经秘密开发了一整年。这一年被 Christopher 定义为“探索期”。在这个阶段，团队不受任何现有用户的束缚，自由地尝试各种疯狂的想法，添加了无数的功能，探索产品的边界。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，就在准备推向市场的前夕，团队做了一个痛苦的决定：砍掉 50% 已经开发完成的代码和功能。这听起来简直是资源浪费，但这正是“利用期”的关键动作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Christopher 解释说，在探索期，你只是在寻找解决问题的“形状”。当你大概摸清了这个形状后，必须进入打磨阶段。如果你保留了所有探索期的功能，你就像是在打磨一块奇形怪状的石头，永远无法使其发光。只有狠心砍掉那 50% 不那么核心、不那么完美的功能，你才能将剩余的 50% 精力集中在真正的核心价值上，将其从“粗糙的形状”打磨成“完美的钻石”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“只有砍掉那平庸的 50%，你才能集中精力将核心打磨成完美的钻石。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种操作在产品发布后几乎是不可能完成的。一旦有了用户，每一个功能——哪怕是多余的——都会有一小撮死忠粉。如果你在发布后试图砍掉一半功能，用户会抗议，社区会暴动。因此，这种大规模的“做减法”，必须且只能在发布前完成。很多时候，你其实已经拥有了 PMF，只是被那 50% 的杂音掩盖了。砍掉杂音，PMF 自然会显现。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统化反馈循环</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有创始人都知道要“和用户交谈”，但真正做到的寥寥无几。原因很简单：太麻烦了。安排时间、发送邀请、调试设备，这些繁琐的流程构成了极高的“激活能量”。为了解决这个问题，Christopher 的策略是将反馈系统化，使其成为公司日常运作的一部分。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“与用户交谈是产品的生命线。如果安排访谈很麻烦，你就不会常做。必须将访谈系统化，变成像呼吸一样自然的事。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在他之前的创业项目 Socratic（一款教育 App）中，他为了观察高中生如何使用产品，想出了一个绝妙的办法：每周二和周四，公司会邀请一组高中生来办公室“做作业”。公司支付报酬，学生们只需要坐在那里完成自己的课业。产品团队不需要刻意安排访谈，随时可以走到学生身边，观察他们遇到难题时的反应，或者把新功能展示给他们看。这种“随叫随到”的反馈环境，让产品的迭代速度有了质的飞跃。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Granola，由于是远程办公且面向职场人，他们调整了策略。团队每周有四天都安排了固定的用户视频访谈时段。这些时段对全公司开放，任何设计师或工程师如果对某个功能有疑问，不需要自己去约用户，只需要跳进正在进行的 Zoom 会议，就能直接听到用户的声音。这种低门槛的机制，保证了用户反馈不再是偶尔的“加餐”，而是每天的主食。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">停止收集冗余反馈</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在传统的大公司里，产品经理往往需要收集几十份问卷，制作精美的 PPT，证明“80% 的用户都觉得这个按钮难用”，才能推动开发团队去修改。但在 Christopher 看来，这是极大的浪费。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“你不需要 10 个人告诉你同一个按钮很困惑。如果第一个用户卡住了，且原因很明显，立即去修复它。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果在访谈中，你看到第一个用户在使用原型时卡住了，而且原因显而易见（比如他试图把圆形积木塞进方形孔里），那么正确的做法是立即停止测试，去修复它。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要浪费时间等下一个人来验证这个已知的错误。立即修复的好处在于，当下一个用户进来时，你不再是验证已知的 Bug，而是有机会发现全新的问题。这种“单点修正”的原则，极大地压缩了反馈的密度和价值，让每一次访谈都能挖掘出新的增量信息。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">保持怀疑、批判和诚实</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户访谈中最大的陷阱就是“礼貌”。人类是社会性动物，当面对创造者时，本能反应是给予赞美和鼓励。当用户说“这很棒”、“我肯定会用它”时，他们可能只是想让你感觉好一点，或者是为了尽快结束访谈拿到礼品卡。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“从负面反馈中寻找真相，正面反馈往往是误导性的噪音。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Christopher 的建议非常激进：彻底忽略所有正面的话。如果用户说“我会买”，不要信。相反，你要做的是“负向挖掘”。你要像侦探一样，专注于观察用户那一瞬间的迟疑、困惑的眼神，或者他们没有去点的那些功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以通过挑战用户来获取真相：“如果是你，你会怎么做？”当他们回答后，继续追问：“真的吗？你不觉得这样操作很累吗？”迫使用户跳出礼貌的社交面具，面对真实的使用场景。只有在负面反馈中，你才能找到改进产品的金矿；而正面反馈，通常只是误导你自我感觉良好的噪音。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用保守的指标</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在数据分析上，Granola 也是“自虐”型的。很多 App 会把“打开应用”或者“浏览页面”算作日活（DAU），这很容易让团队产生一种虚幻的繁荣感。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);padding-left: 12px;margin: 24px 0px;font-style: italic;background: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“不要因为用户打开了 App 就沾沾自喜。这很容易让你产生幻觉，以为自己做得很好。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Granola 对“活跃用户”的定义有着严苛的标准：用户必须在当天创建了一个新的会议，并且该会议至少包含了 5 分钟的转录内容。如果用户只是进来看看历史记录，或者录了 1 分钟就关掉了，对不起，你不算活跃用户。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种极其保守的指标设定，强迫团队去面对真实的产品价值。它剥离了所有好奇的围观者和误操作的流量，剩下的数据反映了真正从产品中获得价值的人群。只有面对这样赤裸的真相，团队才不会给自己找借口，才能专注于解决那些阻碍用户深度使用的真正问题。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">相信你的直觉而非反馈</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然 Christopher 强调倾听用户，但他同样强调：不要盲从用户。这听起来矛盾，实则是产品哲学的辩证统一。用户不仅会撒谎，还会相互矛盾。张三想要更多的自定义选项，李四想要更极简的界面。如果你把所有用户的需求列成一个清单照单全收，你的产品就会变成一个四不像的缝合怪。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);padding-left: 12px;margin: 24px 0px;font-style: italic;background: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“用户不仅不知道自己想要什么，甚至不同用户的需求是完全冲突的。如果只是把用户需求列个清单照着做，产品会变得支离破碎。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的洞察来自于将大量的用户反馈内化，在脑海中建立一个“用户模拟器”。当你与数百个用户深入交谈后，你不需要每次都去问用户，你只需要闭上眼睛问自己：“如果我把这个按钮移到这里，Nancy 会怎么想？Bob 会怎么骂？”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">你应该利用这种内化的直觉来做决定。产品愿景必须高于用户具体的琐碎要求。Granola 的愿景是“极简设计”，那么即便有用户要求增加复杂的功能栏，如果这违背了极简的初衷，你也应该坚定地拒绝。你是产品的总编辑，而不是用户需求的速记员。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">缩短反馈循环</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，一切方法论的底座是“速度”。Christopher 提到了“方孔圆钉”的教训：如果你花了一个月时间开发一个功能，发布后发现用户完全误解了它的用法，就像把圆形积木硬塞进方形孔里，那么这一个月的时间就彻底浪费了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">更糟糕的是“遗忘曲线”。如果反馈周期太长，比如一个月后才收到反馈，你甚至已经忘了当初做这个设计决策时的思考逻辑是什么了。这会导致你无法有效地进行复盘和迭代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Arial, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); border-left: 4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112); padding-left: 12px; margin: 24px 0px; font-style: italic; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">“反馈循环越快，你的直觉进化得越快，产品就能越快逼近 PMF。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">制胜的关键在于尽量缩短从“产生想法”到“获得用户验证”的时间。反馈循环越快，你的直觉进化得越快，你的“用户模拟器”就越精准，产品就能以最快的速度逼近那个神秘的 PMF。在 Granola 的故事里，PMF 不是等待来的，而是用极速的循环和残酷的取舍“跑”出来的。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：PMF 是设计出来的</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Granola 的案例打破了我们对“MVP（最小可行性产品）”的某种刻板误读——即必须发布一个粗糙的半成品去试错。它证明了，通过精密的反馈系统和自我博弈，PMF 完全可以在发布的第一天就被设计出来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Christopher 并没有什么魔法，他只是把那些最难坚持的基本功做到了：克制增加功能的欲望、无视虚荣的赞美指标、建立像呼吸一样自然的反馈机制。在 AI 让构建产品变得如此容易的今天，这种“慢下来”打磨产品灵魂的能力，反而成了最稀缺的壁垒。希望 Granola 的剧本能给你勇气，在下一次发布前，试着砍掉那一半平庸的功能，去打磨那颗真正的钻石。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“How to Build a Product that Hits PMF on Day 1”丨Granola Co-founder Christopher Pedregal</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\">原视频：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hbGQaAXZ5UU\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hbGQaAXZ5UU</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Granola 创始人分享了如何通过赋予产品灵魂、狠心精简功能、系统化用户反馈以及坚持严苛指标，在产品发布首日即实现 PMF 的实战方法论。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Granola 创始人分享了如何通过赋予产品灵魂、狠心精简功能、系统化用户反馈以及坚持严苛指标，在产品发布首日即实现 PMF 的实战方法论。",
  "summary": "本文深度拆解了 AI 会议笔记工具 Granola 创始人的产品哲学。与传统的“快速发布、粗糙迭代”不同，Granola 强调在发布前通过一年的“探索期”摸索形状，并在发布前夕通过“50% 法则”砍掉平庸功能，确保产品以“完成体”面世。文章详细介绍了其系统化的用户反馈机制，包括建立低门槛的访谈环境、停止收集冗余反馈、专注于负面信号以及设定极其保守的活跃用户指标。创始人认为，PMF 不是运气，而是通过内化用户需求、缩短反馈循环并坚持产品愿景，在设计阶段就精准预判并实现的。这种“慢下来”打磨核心价值的策略，使其在竞争激烈的 AI 赛道脱颖而出。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "伟大的产品应具备一致的‘灵魂’与价值观。",
      "explanation": "产品不应是功能的堆砌，而应像人一样拥有连贯的性格。避免组织架构式设计导致的割裂感，让用户在任何交互环节都能感受到统一的内核。"
    },
    {
      "point": "实施 50% 法则，在发布前狠心精简非核心功能。",
      "explanation": "在探索期后，必须砍掉一半平庸的代码，才能集中精力将核心价值打磨成钻石。这种大规模减法在拥有用户后将难以实施。"
    },
    {
      "point": "建立系统化、低门槛的反馈循环，让访谈像呼吸一样自然。",
      "explanation": "通过固定访谈时段、全员参与等机制降低反馈的‘激活能量’。一旦发现明显的单点错误应立即修复，而非等待更多样本验证。"
    },
    {
      "point": "忽略正面礼貌性反馈，专注于挖掘负面真相。",
      "explanation": "用户往往会因为礼貌而撒谎，只有观察其困惑、迟疑或挑战其真实意愿，才能获得改进产品的金矿，避免被噪音误导。"
    },
    {
      "point": "设定极其保守的活跃指标，强迫团队面对真实价值。",
      "explanation": "不以打开应用为日活，而是定义极高门槛的价值行为（如创建 5 分钟以上转录）。这能剥离虚假繁荣，让团队专注于解决核心问题。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "用户不仅不知道自己想要什么，甚至不同用户的需求是完全冲突的。",
    "只有砍掉那平庸的 50%，你才能集中精力将核心打磨成完美的钻石。",
    "如果你需要 10 个人告诉你同一个按钮很困惑，那你就是在浪费时间。",
    "从负面反馈中寻找真相，正面反馈往往是误导性的噪音。",
    "反馈循环越快，你的直觉进化得越快，产品就能越快逼近 PMF。"
  ],
